{"tid":1513694,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"距離831仲有幾日，大家要落地d用番 69 612 818既力度去宣傳","createTime":"2019-08-28T12:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T00:01:38.000Z","uid":231583,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"6e912c69260c6141ae7d2d7ff0cf152103c6394e","tid":1513694,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:25:45.000Z","msg":"91已經有呂麗瑤巴打騎劫左宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />92 93三罷仍然有時間宣傳，所以我認為我地需要主力先谷831人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後仲可以用831 91遊行同和你飛個時主力宣傳埋三罷<br />\n<br />\n831係反對支那人大831決定，表明我地&quot;爭取普選決心&quot;既一次遊行，人數依然相當重要(但唔好墮入追數陷阱執著於人數)，而且今次終點係中聯辦，如無意外今次一定會出反對通知書，分分鐘禁止埋集會，呢個情況下更加需要大力d宣傳和理非們先會肯出黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地唔好只留係同溫層宣傳，留係連登推十次post都未必及得上你出面派一張傳單</span><br />\n連儂牆、連儂電視、傳單、babykindom、香討、facebook、whatsapp、ig story、air drop、長輩圖、乜都好，快d一傳十十傳百出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好學班垃圾政府同送中派咁留係自己同溫層呀<br />\n美國復會在即啦，政府已經痴到想玩埋緊急法，呢個時候懶唔去文宣=自取滅亡<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懇求大家最後呢兩日一齊落地d宣傳831</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/RA6qYoP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRA6qYoP.png&h=7d0c5e67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">831 3pm 遮打花園見！</span>"},{"pid":"50c69a2e17f93401f511a658db34f4516279de28","tid":1513694,"uid":63045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:26:11.000Z","msg":"[置頂-連登改變世界]929全球集會抗赤納粹，召喚攬炒巴，G20巴，動畫巴，各文宣巴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推上頂，香港人我地要一齊做<br />\n#Chinazi<br />\n#ProtectOurCountry<br />\n#StandwithHongKong<br />\n#NomadeinChina<br />\n<br />\n大家申請咗Twitter AC未，記得用新email注冊"},{"pid":"fc4650bf17c48b9e7b60458c0eabd41cb93439f5","tid":1513694,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:26:34.000Z","msg":"派傳單<br />\n放映會<br />\nwechat<br />\nwhatsapp <br />\nfacebook<br />\nairdrop <br />\n長輩圖<br />\n貼街招<br />\n入信箱<br />\n諗到咩文宣方法都去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就洗緊自己幢樓喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />派傳單"},{"pid":"53ea68b3a60305d0ef80df170d55247c1e714e41","tid":1513694,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xyKLSLG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxyKLSLG.jpg&h=6597f1bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12adee48e782f7e7d349645448c1ca94a3a3e7c8","tid":1513694,"uid":238275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCBypV8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCBypV8.gif&h=d3183b47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCBypV8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCBypV8.gif&h=d3183b47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCBypV8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCBypV8.gif&h=d3183b47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCBypV8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCBypV8.gif&h=d3183b47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCBypV8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCBypV8.gif&h=d3183b47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCBypV8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCBypV8.gif&h=d3183b47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCBypV8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCBypV8.gif&h=d3183b4